

                           [help shout]
-----------------------=========+=========-----------------------                          

Usage: shout <message>
 
 This is a public channel. This channel is similar to the emergency
channel in that it is used to get a wizards attention or possible
someone capable of helping. Do not abuse this channel, although
its use is not as strict as that of emergency. To take yourself
off of this channel type 'muffle shout'. To see who is on this
channel type,'shout list'. To turn this channel on type,
'channel shout'.                      

